title: Linkin Park - Live in St. Paul, MN 2-13-2008
description:
2nd SBD show of the North American arena tour, once again this is the full digipack with tourbook and photos. Thanks to Dark_Adolescent for uploading the show on Megaupload, and Elycia for sharing the photos!

St. Paul, Minnesota
